FIG. 11 is a front elevation view of the embodiment of FIG. 10 further including a safety chain with a connection link member comprising the hook of FIGS. 4a, 4b and 5 releasably attached to the bracket of FIG. 8;


FIG. 12 is a diagrammatic representation of the installation steps of the safety chain of FIG. 11 to the bracket of FIG. 8;


FIG. 13 is a more detailed view of the view at step 3 of FIG. 12a useful for explaining certain principles of the present invention; and


FIG. 14 is a view similar to that of FIG. 13 but with a single S-hook of FIG. 2 inserted into the bracket opening.
